  </tr>

</table>

<p class="heading"><a name="links"></a>Links:</p>

<ul>

  <li><a href="http://www.leonardbernstein.com" target="_blank">The Official 

    Bernstein Site</a><br>
	
	This huge site is presented by Classical Insites. A single source for 

    information on Bernstein, lists of events, and links to commercial sites. 

    Start at the Home/Studio, a virtual tour of Bernstein's life including pictures 

    and memorabilia, letters, sound samples and video, and special essays on various 

    topics. If you enjoy Bernstein and his music, or even (as Bernstein did) puzzles, 

    this site will keep you busy for days.

</ul>

